paths: Obvious paths: east, southwest, west, northwest
description: A particularly stubborn scrub tree clings to life here, somehow finding sustenance in the mud.  It has but a few leaves, and its trunk is bare of bark from the ground up to the span of a dwarf.  A mud-spattered raven perches on one branch, huddled against the damp breeze.
title: [Noman's Land, Urgh Pens]
